---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'March 13, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="OPX Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-brand-muted mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8 text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          OPX ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website opxhq.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or subscribe to our newsletter.
        </p>
        <p>
          By using our site, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-text mb-2">Information you provide:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Email address (when subscribing to our newsletter)</li>
          <li>Any information you voluntarily submit via forms or contact</li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-text mb-2 mt-4">Automatically collected:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Log data (IP address, browser type, pages visited, time/date)</li>
          <li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies</li>
          <li>Analytics data (via privacy-respecting analytics tools)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To send our newsletter and content updates (email subscribers only)</li>
          <li>To improve and optimize our website</li>
          <li>To understand how users engage with our content</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">4. Email & Newsletter</h2>
        <p>
          If you subscribe to our newsletter via Beehiiv, your email is processed by Beehiiv in accordance with their privacy policy. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in any newsletter email.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">5. Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>
          Some links on this site are affiliate links. Clicking these links does not share your personal data with us, but may be tracked by the affiliate platform (e.g., Amazon, supplement retailers).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">6. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We may use cookies for basic site functionality and analytics. You can control cookie settings through your browser. Disabling cookies may affect some site features.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">7. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may use the following third-party services, each with their own privacy policies:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Beehiiv (email newsletter platform)</li>
          <li>Netlify (website hosting)</li>
          <li>Analytics providers</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights including:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Access to your personal data</li>
          <li>Correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">To exercise these rights, contact us at: <a href="mailto:hello@opxhq.com" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">hello@opxhq.com</a></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our site is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will post the updated version with a new "Last Updated" date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@opxhq.com" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">hello@opxhq.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
